{"arkId":"cl010112520","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010112520","modified ":"2025-12-12","title":"Coffret : Sc\u00e8nes de l\u0027Enfance du Christ","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Coffret : Sc\u00e8nes de l\u0027Enfance du Christ"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : dynastie des Carolingiens (752-987) (Occident-\u003Emoyen \u00e2ge-\u003Ehaut moyen \u00e2ge)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 870 - 880 (attribution d\u0027apr\u00e8s style)","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 501 - Charlemagne, Vitrine 6 Paradis terrestre","room":"Salle 501, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":870,"endYear":880,"imprecision":"vers","text":"2e moiti\u00e9 du IXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Seconde \u00e9cole de Metz","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"MRR 75","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"coffret","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Les sc\u00e8nes de l\u0027enfance du Christ sont r\u00e9parties sur toute la surface du coffret rectangulaire surmont\u00e9 d\u0027un haut couvercle. Une monture m\u00e9tallique recouvrait \u00e0 l\u0027origine les bordures des panneaux comme en t\u00e9moignent les trous de fixation.\r\nSur la face longitudinale, sur le couvercle, l\u0027Adoration des rois mages que l\u0027on identifie gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 leurs bonnets phrygiens, et en dessous, sur la caisse, H\u00e9rode accueillant les rois mages venus lui annoncer la naissance divine.\r\nA gauche, sur le couvercle, un ange appara\u00eet \u00e0 Joseph endormi, sur la caisse, la Visitation.\r\nA droite, sur le couvercle, un ange appara\u00eet devant les rois mages endormis pour leur conseiller de repartir par un autre chemin, sur la caisse, un ange appara\u00eet \u00e0 Marie (Annonciation?).\r\nAutre face longitudinale, sur le couvercle, Fuite en Egypte, et sur la caisse Nativit\u00e9 et Pr\u00e9sentation au Temple.","inscriptions":"Etiquette : \r ; A l\u0027encre, sur une \u00e9tiquette ronde bord\u00e9e de bleu : \u0022902\u0022 ; \u00e9tiquettes rectangulaires : \u0022A 69\u0022 et \u0022N 1065\u0022.","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"22,5","displayDimension":"22,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"13,2","displayDimension":"13,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"8,5","displayDimension":"8,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"24","displayDimension":"24 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"22,2","displayDimension":"22,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":5,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"16,3","displayDimension":"16,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":6,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"15,2","displayDimension":"15,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":7,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"14,5","displayDimension":"14,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":8,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : ivoire d\u0027\u00e9l\u00e9phant = d\u00e9fense d\u0027\u00e9l\u00e9phant","placeOfCreation":"Metz (Lorraine-\u003EMoselle)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],